OL,3,CPlymouth Argyle striker targeted with
OL,4,C'vile racist abuse'
OL,6,FPlymouth Argyle have contacted police
OL,7,Fafter striker Bim Pepple was subjected
OL,8,Fto "vile racist abuse" on social media.
OL,10,FPepple, 22, received insulting direct
OL,11,Fmessages on Instagram after he missed
OL,12,Fa penalty in the Pilgrims' 2-0 victory
OL,13,Fat home to Cheltenham Town on Tuesday
OL,14,F2 September.
OL,16,FThe club said screenshots of the
OL,17,Fmessages have been shared with the
OL,18,Fpolice and Meta, the company which
OL,19,Fowns Instagram.
