OL,6,F"We will do everything possible to
OL,7,Fsupport Bim and hold those responsible
OL,8,Fto account," the club said in a
OL,9,Fstatement.
OL,11,FIt added that the messages were sent
OL,12,Fby "small-minded individuals" and that
OL,13,Fabuse of any kind will not be
OL,14,Ftolerated.
OL,16,FThe club added: "We will continue to
OL,17,Fchampion the various activities across
OL,18,Ffootball, including the EFL's
OL,19,F'Together Against Racism' campaign, as
OL,20,Fclearly the message isn't getting
OL,21,Fthrough.
